1
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:25,200
<i>♪ I have a heart and know how to love ♪</i>

2
00:00:25,240 --> 00:00:29,760
<i>♪ Especially when I see you</i>
<i>I keep seeing the scenes ♪</i>

3
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:33,200
<i>♪ From when we were together ♪</i>

4
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:36,400
<i>♪ But I keep seeing you in my head ♪</i>

5
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:41,120
<i>♪ My broken heart hasn't recovered ♪</i>

6
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:43,720
<i>♪ So I hurt you ♪</i>

7
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:49,040
<i>♪ Even though I have to</i>
<i>Make myself watch you cry ♪</i>

8
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:55,320
<i>♪ I hate it but I still do it ♪</i>

9
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:59,280
<i>♪ I keep picking at scabs to hurt you ♪</i>

10
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:06,800
<i>♪ I want to escape</i>
<i>But it feels like walking in circles ♪</i>

11
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:11,560
<i>♪ In the end I hurt myself</i>
<i>Keeping my love hidden ♪</i>

12
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:14,800
<i>♪ I can't walk away even if I want to ♪</i>

13
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:19,800
<i>♪ My love must be hidden</i>
<i>I can hardly stand it ♪</i>

14
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:22,720
♪ It's torture when you cry ♪

15
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:26,600
<i>♪ The more you're hurt ♪</i>

16
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:30,680
<i>♪ The weaker my heart becomes ♪</i>

17
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:37,160
<i>♪ I try not to love you</i>
<i>Holding back my tears while saying goodbye ♪</i>

18
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:41,400
<i>♪ But I could never do it for real ♪</i>

19
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:07,120
<i>Attention please. Code 000 at the ER.</i>

20
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:10,600
<i>Attention please. Code 000 at the ER.</i>

21
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,720
Where's my daughter?

22
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,080
Can you speak English?

23
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:15,520
I want to go find my daughter. Where's my daughter?

24
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,920
-Can anyone here speak Chinese?
-No, Doctor.

25
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,360
Could you please speak English?

26
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,600
I want to go find my daughter.

27
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,160
Calm down please. I'll ask them for you.

28
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:26,480
She came in with her daughter.
Do you know where she is?

29
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:29,240
She's in Bed 3. Dr. Pannaorn is with her.

30
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:32,400
Your daughter is already in the care of the doctors.

31
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:34,480
Don't worry. We will do our best.

32
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:37,760
Okay. Please help her.
Please save my daughter.

33
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:40,960
In this case I suspect an inhalation burn

34
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:44,840
and a second-degree burn of about
5% on her right limbs.

35
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,760
I'll leave you to it. I have another case to tend to.

36
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:47,760
Sure.

37
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:51,720
The patient has an inhalation burn.
Her blood pressure is dropping.

38
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:54,600
Prepare intubation and start a central line.

39
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:55,640
Yes, Doctor.

40
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,800
Look at you guys.

41
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,200
You look like you've just fought a war?

42
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:25,240
Trauma patients came in droves.

43
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:27,280
Thankfully Lada helped me

44
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:29,160
or else I would've been screwed.

45
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,640
Hey,

46
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:36,160
since you're great at everything,

47
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:38,440
study emergency medicine
and come work with me.

48
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,000
Very funny.

49
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,920
What about my dermatology ward?

50
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,160
Just work in both wards.

51
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:47,600
Bow.

52
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:51,960
Just because she's the owner's daughter,
you expect her to work in two wards?

53
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,440
She's gonna die as it is.

54
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,880
Don't die yet.

55
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,800
Refresh with coffee first.

56
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,560
And go back to work.

57
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,040
-You're the devil.
-You're the devil.

58
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,320
Not so fast.

59
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,600
I'm a nurse.

60
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,960
A nurse.

61
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,360
Yes.

62
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,440
Ah, just now

63
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:15,640
the staff in the ER were talking

64
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:18,079
how Dr. Lada was such a badass

65
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:21,079
for talking to a Chinese patient
without using an interpreter.

66
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,160
Of course.

67
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:26,240
She was an exchange student.
Speaks almost every language.

68
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,720
Except...

69
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,120
love language, right?

70
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:34,000
That's why Dr. Lada's still single.

71
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,120
Ms. Rose?

72
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:54,200
When am I scheduled to do my round today?

73
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,600
Uh...

74
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,840
You're not.

75
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:59,240
You have to shoot a commercial today.

76
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:11,040
Dr. Fahlada, please wait a moment.

77
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,640
The presenter is coming.

78
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,920
Sure.

79
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,880
The presenter is here!

80
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,880
Oh, hello there!

81
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,840
I missed you, Doc.

82
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,800
I'm sorry.

83
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:24,200
-I'm so sorry.
-It's okay.

84
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,000
Your way.

85
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,280
How can someone be that pretty?

86
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,880
Thank you.

87
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,200
You're Thai?

88
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,640
Yes.

89
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,200
I'm Thai.

90
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,560
Your coffee.

91
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,720
Thank you.

92
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:34,520
I'm so glad to meet a Thai person here.

93
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:37,360
Ever since I got here,
I haven't met Thai people.

94
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,400
It's been so lonely.

95
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,080
Always felt I was by myself.

96
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:44,640
What do you study here?

97
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,960
I'm studying management. What about you?

98
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,760
I'm studying medicine.

99
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:56,280
Wow, you're a doctor too?

100
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,120
-What's so excited about that?
-Duh.

101
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:03,040
I haven't met a doctor this beautiful.

102
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:08,400
You say that like you're not beautiful.

103
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:17,040
You're the first person to say I'm beautiful.

104
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,560
People usually say I'm...

105
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,600
childish.

106
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:25,000
So...

107
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,080
if I call you...

108
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,480
"Doc,"

109
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,760
will that be okay?

110
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,480
I think it's cool.

111
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,120
As you wish.

112
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,360
Call me whatever you want.

113
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,880
And if I'm into you,

114
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,960
what should I do?

115
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,160
Do nothing.

116
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:59,400
Go back to work first.

117
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,040
Sorry.

118
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,280
Okay.

119
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,040
Hi.

120
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:37,760
What would you like to order?

121
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,200
Can I get...

122
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,480
Chocolate cake.

123
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,640
Okay, what else?

124
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,720
Can I get...

125
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,320
hot milk?

126
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,000
Two please.

127
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,920
-Thank you.
-Just a moment please.

128
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,960
Thank you.

129
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,000
Let's take a photo.

130
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:00,680
Come on.

131
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,960
Get more at the top.

132
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,840
Huh?

133
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:08,640
Hm?

134
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,360
Kiss.

135
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,360
Here's your order.

136
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,960
Thank you.

137
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,240
Thank you.

138
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,040
It looks so yummy.

139
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,840
Okay, just a moment please.

140
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:25,920
Again. One more.

141
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,000
I love seeing something like that.

142
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,600
It's a feast for the eyes.

143
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,680
Doc?

144
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,560
Have you eaten?

145
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:21,080
I got this for you in case you're hungry.
I'll leave it here.

146
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,600
Bye-bye.

147
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:32,360
She's a menace.

148
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:36,360
 DON'T FORGET TO EAT.
 DOCTORS CAN GET SICK TOO.

149
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,520
Here's your coffee.

150
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,600
Hey!

151
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,200
How much?

152
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:49,040
What do you mean "How much?"
I'm not the kind of person you're looking for.

153
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:50,920
-Calm down.
-What...

154
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:51,920
What happened?

155
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:54,040
-Nothing.
-He touched me

156
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,200
and he asked me how much.

157
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,800
You have any proof?

158
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:05,040
I know that all Asian girls
are lying and ask about money.

159
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,840
Bitch.

160
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:09,960
Hey, watch your language.

161
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:12,800
Did you forget we have CCTV cameras here?

162
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,960
Over there and there.

163
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,120
If you have problem with Asian girls,

164
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:20,360
you can contact my lawyer.

165
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:31,040
I've changed jobs many times.

166
00:12:31,680 --> 00:12:34,400
And I've always been insulted and bullied.

167
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:37,000
But I never gave in so I punched back.

168
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,400
Hey.

169
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,040
You assault other people.

170
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,960
Aren't you afraid of getting sued?

171
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,520
I would run.

172
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:48,520
I'd run like hell and disappear.

173
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,880
So let me ask you honestly.

174
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:58,400
Why do you have to work this hard?

175
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,800
Are you putting yourself through school?

176
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:02,960
No.

177
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,640
My parents pay for it.

178
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:08,040
But I wanted to lighten their burden.

179
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:10,320
The cost of living here is high.

180
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,320
So...

181
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:17,720
if there's anything I can do, let me know.

182
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,960
Can you take me in and support me?

183
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:27,920
Think of it as helping an innocent kid.

184
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:31,920
I'm kidding.

185
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:48,960
Earn?

186
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,680
Why are you sleeping here?

187
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:55,560
Well,

188
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:58,680
my roommate's boyfriend came by

189
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,640
so I...

190
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,800
came down to read.

191
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,920
Are you sick?

192
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:12,200
A little headache.

193
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,960
I don't think it's little.

194
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,600
You're burning up.

195
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:24,240
Why don't you come to my apartment?

196
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:37,320
Did you know Son-in-law eggs were my favorite?

197
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,440
What's your favorite?

198
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,200
You.

199
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:20,120
Earn! Come eat.

200
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:26,520
Son-in-law eggs.

201
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:28,400
Ow.

202
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:29,560
Stop.

203
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:31,560
Yours is rice soup.

204
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,800
So you can take your med.

205
00:15:34,040 --> 00:15:35,040
Jeez.

206
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:38,440
Did you know Son-in-law eggs were my favorite?

207
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:39,960
My all-time favorite.

208
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:42,880
But I haven't had them since I got here.

209
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:44,960
What's your favorite?

210
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:46,760
You.

211
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:55,960
Stir-fried glass noodles.

212
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:59,320
I see, stir-fried glass noodles.

213
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:04,480
If so, I'll learn to cook
mean stir-fried glass noodles

214
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:06,520
and make it for you every day, okay?

215
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:11,360
Then I'm gonna learn to cook
mean Son-in-law eggs for you too.

216
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,600
Maybe I get to be the daughter-in-law.

217
00:16:16,560 --> 00:16:17,560
Huh?

218
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:18,840
Huh?

219
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:30,760
-Hello.
-Hello.

220
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:32,080
These flowers are for you.

221
00:16:32,560 --> 00:16:34,120
Thank you.

222
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,720
Valentine's Day.

223
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:38,080
Can you sign for me here please?

224
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:40,280
Someone must have sent her flowers.

225
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:42,440
-Okay.
-Thank you. Have a nice day.

226
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:43,920
Thank you. Have a nice day.

227
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:12,440
They're pretty.

228
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:14,680
You like them?

229
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:18,960
They're just pretty.

230
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:23,800
They're for you.

231
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:30,200
Happy Valentine's Day.

232
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:34,120
Doc!

233
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:38,240
They're for me?

234
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:45,240
Please date me,

235
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:48,320
my stubborn girl.

236
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:54,160
I will.

237
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,440
Hello,

238
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,960
my love.

239
00:19:57,760 --> 00:19:59,880
Hello, my heart.

240
00:20:12,960 --> 00:20:18,080
MY HEART

241
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:26,120
You're adorable.

242
00:20:29,760 --> 00:20:31,480
Focus on your study.

243
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,800
I love only you.

244
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:48,160
I'm back.

245
00:20:48,560 --> 00:20:50,760
Oh, you're back?

246
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:55,240
Look. This is my dream house.

247
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:59,240
It's my dream that one day I will own this house.

248
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:01,160
It must be expensive.

249
00:21:03,080 --> 00:21:05,280
It is, but...

250
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:07,960
if I work and start saving up now,

251
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:10,760
I should be able to afford it when I'm 40.

252
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:12,200
Or 50.

253
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:13,960
Sixty.

254
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:15,280
Seventy.

255
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,000
Eighty.

256
00:21:17,360 --> 00:21:19,440
I can't wait until eighty. I'll be too old.

257
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:22,560
I'd rather lying around with my dog and you.

258
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:26,000
Eighty for real?

259
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:45,600
Here.

260
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,240
A jigsaw puzzle?

261
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:49,960
That's right.

262
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:55,080
What's the picture? Can you show it to me?

263
00:21:56,360 --> 00:21:57,200
Secret.

264
00:21:57,560 --> 00:21:58,440
Secret?

265
00:21:59,160 --> 00:22:01,440
When you're done,

266
00:22:02,080 --> 00:22:05,920
you'll find out this picture is very important

267
00:22:06,280 --> 00:22:07,600
to our relationship.

268
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,000
Really?

269
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:10,800
Mm-hm.

270
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:50,960
Thank you.

271
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:53,480
FAHLADA & EARN

272
00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:54,680
Don't open your eyes.

273
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:56,520
Am I gonna crash?

274
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:58,240
-You won't.
-Am I gonna crash?

275
00:22:58,240 --> 00:22:59,720
You won't.

276
00:23:00,760 --> 00:23:03,640
-Close your eyes.
-They're closed. I won't look. Promise.

277
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:06,440
Sorry.

278
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:09,760
Come on. I'll let you see.

279
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:11,040
I'm so excited!

280
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:12,600
One,

281
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:13,840
two,

282
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:14,920
three!

283
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:21,160
Happy birthday to my love!

284
00:23:21,800 --> 00:23:23,640
You made everything yourself?

285
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:25,760
No, I hired someone.

286
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,840
I'm joking.

287
00:23:29,840 --> 00:23:32,040
Of course I made it myself.

288
00:23:33,080 --> 00:23:34,040
Do you like it?

289
00:23:34,080 --> 00:23:36,240
I do. Thank you.

290
00:23:37,120 --> 00:23:38,400
-Here.
-What did you make?

291
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,200
I made this.

292
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:41,960
A banoffee pie.

293
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:44,400
This is my first time making it.

294
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:47,080
I'll feed you.

295
00:23:48,520 --> 00:23:49,520
Here.

296
00:23:49,760 --> 00:23:51,200
I'll give you a big bite.

297
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:53,960
Ah...

298
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,720
You don't like it?

299
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:59,400
I put a lot of effort into this.

300
00:24:00,840 --> 00:24:02,000
Of course I like it.

301
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:03,560
It's made by my girlfriend.

302
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,880
Here you go.

303
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:13,480
Well? Is it good?

304
00:24:15,920 --> 00:24:17,160
You like it, don't you?

305
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:21,320
Ah...

306
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:27,720
Ah...

307
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:29,720
Is it good?

308
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:36,000
Earn?

309
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:37,480
What's wrong?

310
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:39,400
Earn?

311
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:42,680
Earn? Earn?

312
00:24:46,040 --> 00:24:47,040
Earn?

313
00:24:48,840 --> 00:24:49,840
Breathe.

314
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:51,040
It's okay.

315
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:53,200
Earn, are you okay?

316
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:34,720
Doc?

317
00:25:38,280 --> 00:25:39,680
You can't take it off.

318
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:41,680
But it's uncomfortable.

319
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:43,000
You can't.

320
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:44,440
Earn.

321
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,240
It was uncomfortable.

322
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:50,600
You're so stubborn.

323
00:25:53,600 --> 00:25:56,080
Why didn't you tell me
you were allergic to bananas?

324
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:59,800
I didn't want to offend you.

325
00:25:59,840 --> 00:26:01,920
You put a lot of effort into it.

326
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:05,160
I just wanted to surprise you on your birthday.

327
00:26:08,080 --> 00:26:09,480
But it's ruined now.

328
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:14,160
Really?

329
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,160
Says who?

330
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:37,560
Doc!

331
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:43,480
Let me?

332
00:26:47,360 --> 00:26:49,160
You're not allergic to anything here?

333
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:51,440
Doc.

334
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:53,320
You're ruining the moment.

335
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:57,480
Make a wish first.

336
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:28,760
Doc.

337
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:32,480
Wait a sec. This shawl.

338
00:27:33,280 --> 00:27:34,680
Let me put this down.

339
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:44,640
-Do you like it?
-I do.

340
00:27:45,840 --> 00:27:48,120
I had it custom-made.

341
00:27:48,280 --> 00:27:49,720
To represent us.

342
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:55,800
F.E.

343
00:27:56,320 --> 00:27:57,440
Fahlada.

344
00:27:58,600 --> 00:27:59,600
Earn.

345
00:28:02,760 --> 00:28:03,760
You like it?

346
00:28:04,040 --> 00:28:05,040
I do.

347
00:28:05,840 --> 00:28:07,560
I'll put it on you then.

348
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:18,160
Come on.

349
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:32,160
What should we have for dinner, Doc?

350
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:36,240
Anything is fine. Whatever you want, Earn.

351
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:38,520
So...

352
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:40,320
how about Chinese?

353
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,840
Or maybe we should get sushi?

354
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:46,200
At your favorite restaurant.

355
00:28:50,520 --> 00:28:52,400
But I want Son-in-law eggs.

356
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:54,400
Maybe we should make them?

357
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:58,320
Let me study a little.

358
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:02,800
I get you have to study

359
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:06,920
but your non-answers don't tell me
if I have to dress up for dinner...

360
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,320
Doc.

361
00:29:13,920 --> 00:29:17,560
That's your punishment for not letting me study.

362
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:21,880
If that's my punishment,
I'm happy to talk all day long.

363
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:25,600
Stubborn girl.

364
00:29:28,840 --> 00:29:30,480
Oh, you're not studying anymore?

365
00:29:31,280 --> 00:29:33,760
I can't concentrate.

366
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:44,320
Look at this.

367
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:47,640
Who are they?

368
00:29:48,840 --> 00:29:49,920
Lada, of course.

369
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:53,480
Our daughter is turning into a perv...

370
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:56,960
A homosexual.

371
00:29:58,280 --> 00:29:59,280
So what?

372
00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:01,040
What do you mean, "So what?"

373
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:04,320
What do you mean by that?

374
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:07,800
Lada is a daughter of a hospital's owners.

375
00:30:07,840 --> 00:30:09,560
She's going to be a doctor.

376
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:12,440
She'll take over our hospital one day.

377
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:14,960
She's currently dating a woman.

378
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,360
It's her happiness.

379
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,760
But I can't accept it.

380
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:22,920
You're not bothered by this at all, are you?

381
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:26,640
I'm her father.

382
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:29,320
I'm not her owner.

383
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:32,280
And sexual orientation is personal.

384
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:34,160
We shouldn't intervene.

385
00:30:37,360 --> 00:30:38,360
Okay.

386
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,440
That's it then.

387
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:43,520
Let's agree to disagree.

388
00:30:44,360 --> 00:30:46,840
If you're gonna be indifferent,
it's your business.

389
00:30:47,760 --> 00:30:48,960
But I won't allow it.

390
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:51,520
Lada must break up with that girl

391
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:55,440
and marry only the person I choose.

392
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:15,400
Come in.

393
00:31:18,840 --> 00:31:21,320
Lady Russamee, Dr. Wisanu asks to see you.

394
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:26,080
Let him in.

395
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,520
Hello, ma'am.

396
00:31:46,760 --> 00:31:49,800
The specs of a new medical device
for your consideration.

397
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:52,080
It shouldn't be a problem.

398
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:54,360
We've worked together for a long time.

399
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:57,400
I'll let our procurement department
take care of it.

400
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:58,680
Yes.

401
00:31:59,360 --> 00:32:00,400
I'm glad you're here.

402
00:32:02,920 --> 00:32:05,000
I have something important to discuss.

403
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,600
What can I do for you?

404
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,520
It's not that important.

405
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:15,840
I was just wondering
if you've talked to Lada lately.

406
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:21,040
We talk on the phone sometimes.

407
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:22,480
But...

408
00:32:22,600 --> 00:32:24,240
she's been busy lately

409
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:26,040
so she can't talk to me often.

410
00:32:31,720 --> 00:32:33,480
This is just like you.

411
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:36,480
But I just sent her a care package.

412
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:37,880
All her favorites.

413
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:39,160
Jeez, Nu.

414
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:41,600
That's not enough.

415
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:51,000
I'm gonna be honest with you.

416
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:56,600
I have high hopes for you.

417
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:01,000
I want you to be Lada's companion.

418
00:33:02,560 --> 00:33:03,840
Because one day...

419
00:33:04,800 --> 00:33:07,320
Lada will come back and run this hospital.

420
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:10,880
If you marry Lada,

421
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:14,400
it will put my mind at ease.

422
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:19,120
Yes.

423
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,920
I'm trying to score points too.

424
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:23,560
But if it's not good enough,

425
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:25,480
I'm gonna try harder.

426
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:27,240
You can rest assured.

427
00:33:38,560 --> 00:33:39,560
Studying?

428
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:43,680
The exams are coming up
but I'm still not confident.

429
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:46,160
Probably because I've been too stressed lately.

430
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:05,240
When you're stressed, look at this music box.

431
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:09,400
So you'll know you have me
by your side, always supporting you.

432
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:14,840
How adorable.

433
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:17,199
The gift giver...

434
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:18,760
or the figurine?

435
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,320
The figurine.

436
00:34:25,040 --> 00:34:26,960
Can't compete with the gift giver.

437
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:37,679
How adorable.

438
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:39,960
Love you so much I could die.

439
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:41,480
Do you know?

440
00:34:43,520 --> 00:34:44,800
You can't die.

441
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,880
If you die, who would I be with?

442
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:48,520
You can't die.

443
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:50,480
-You can't die.
-You can't die.

444
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,480
You can't die.

445
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:57,560
Shall we play it?

446
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,400
It's my dad.

447
00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:30,480
Hello, Dad.

448
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,720
What's wrong with Mom?

449
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:02,040
Calm down.

450
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:04,400
Earn.

451
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:05,880
Calm down.

452
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:10,640
Your mother's with doctors now.

453
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:15,000
But my dad told me

454
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:19,280
the tumor in her brain was very hard to treat.

455
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:21,760
that I had to prepare for the worst.

456
00:36:22,640 --> 00:36:24,880
What should I do, Doc?

457
00:36:28,120 --> 00:36:29,240
Don't worry.

458
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:32,600
I'll figure how a way to help your mother.

459
00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:43,400
Hello, what's going on, baby?

460
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:45,320
Is this a good time to talk?

461
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,920
I have a big favor to ask.

462
00:36:48,080 --> 00:36:49,840
Of course. What's going on?

463
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,080
Well,

464
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:54,680
I have a patient with a brain tumor

465
00:36:55,360 --> 00:36:56,360
in critical condition.

466
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:59,880
<i>I want her to be treated</i>
<i>with special care in our hospital.</i>

467
00:37:00,640 --> 00:37:01,800
Who is this patient?

468
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:04,880
She's...

469
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:08,040
a mother of my younger schoolmate.

470
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:12,200
Is this person so important

471
00:37:12,680 --> 00:37:15,200
that you called me for help?

472
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:19,520
Let's just say...

473
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:21,960
you have to save her.

474
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:23,360
I'm begging you.

475
00:37:24,080 --> 00:37:25,080
Of course.

476
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,720
What's her name?

477
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:33,480
Just give me her number. I'll take care of it.

478
00:37:34,800 --> 00:37:36,200
Thank you, Mom.

479
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:37,520
I love you.

480
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:39,000
Got it.

481
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:39,960
Love you.

482
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:41,280
Love you back.

483
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:00,200
Don't worry.

484
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:03,240
Mom! Dad!

485
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,760
-Earn?
-Earn?

486
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:08,960
How did you get here? I missed you so much.

487
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:12,600
I was worried about you so I came back.

488
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:16,960
Oh, I missed you so much.

489
00:38:17,080 --> 00:38:18,880
-I really did.
-Come here.

490
00:38:19,680 --> 00:38:21,720
I'm not that sick.

491
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:24,800
It's nothing. Just a mass in her head.

492
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:28,800
How are you feeling? Do you get bad headaches?

493
00:38:29,040 --> 00:38:31,880
Not anymore. They're not so bad now.

494
00:38:32,560 --> 00:38:36,040
I actually made my peace with it.
I was gonna refuse treatment

495
00:38:36,080 --> 00:38:38,880
because surgery doesn't guarantee I'll be cured.

496
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:41,520
But out of the blue
I got a call from this hospital,

497
00:38:41,560 --> 00:38:43,160
telling me to get treated here.

498
00:38:43,160 --> 00:38:46,560
And they said your friend arranged everything.

499
00:38:48,160 --> 00:38:51,040
Plus, they had her stay in a VIP room

500
00:38:51,160 --> 00:38:53,920
and got her the best doctors.

501
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:55,920
Who's your friend?

502
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:02,280
She's someone who takes care of me
while I'm over there.

503
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:04,280
She's so good to me.

504
00:39:09,720 --> 00:39:10,800
I'll take it for you.

505
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:13,880
Hello?

506
00:39:18,720 --> 00:39:20,360
To come down and meet who?

507
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:41,360
Hello.

508
00:39:50,600 --> 00:39:51,600
You're Earn?

509
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:53,640
Yes.

510
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:58,400
Lada called me

511
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:01,600
to arrange your mother's treatment.

512
00:40:02,640 --> 00:40:03,640
Yes.

513
00:40:04,040 --> 00:40:05,480
She already told me.

514
00:40:06,080 --> 00:40:07,840
I have to thank you.

515
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:08,640
Don't.

516
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,600
I did because I had to.

517
00:40:16,360 --> 00:40:18,520
I read your mother's treatment history.

518
00:40:19,520 --> 00:40:23,440
And I'll have a team of
my best doctors treat your mother.

519
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:28,760
But there's an understanding we must reach first.

520
00:40:31,240 --> 00:40:32,240
What's that?

521
00:40:39,480 --> 00:40:41,800
I know you're dating my daughter.

522
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,800
And I understand

523
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,880
we can't choose who we love.

524
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:50,880
But Lada is my best hope

525
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:53,520
and the most qualified person

526
00:40:54,160 --> 00:40:56,720
to take over our hospital.

527
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:00,600
What...

528
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:04,520
What do you want me to do?

529
00:41:08,160 --> 00:41:09,760
Break up with Lada.

530
00:41:11,960 --> 00:41:14,280
Because the love between you and Lada

531
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:16,440
will never come to fruition.

532
00:41:18,520 --> 00:41:19,760
You might be too young

533
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,480
to understand this.

534
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:23,920
I know my daughter.

535
00:41:25,600 --> 00:41:27,360
Lada gets lonely easily.

536
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:31,120
So she found someone to be near her.

537
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:34,680
And she's well aware

538
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:39,280
that after graduation, she has to come back
and marry someone I've chosen for her.

539
00:41:41,600 --> 00:41:43,080
You might be unaware

540
00:41:44,600 --> 00:41:46,320
that before she went abroad,

541
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:49,080
she'd already started dating Dr. Wisanu.

542
00:41:53,280 --> 00:41:54,640
FROM: WISANU P.
TO: FAHLADA T.

543
00:41:54,720 --> 00:41:58,240
<i>Doc, you've got a package from Thailand.</i>

544
00:41:58,560 --> 00:42:00,520
It says the sender is...

545
00:42:00,800 --> 00:42:02,680
Mr. Wisanu. Who's that?

546
00:42:04,560 --> 00:42:05,920
It's nothing.

547
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:11,760
Uh...

548
00:42:13,280 --> 00:42:14,880
Let me take this call.

549
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:22,000
Hello, Nu.

550
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:24,360
Yes.

551
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:30,480
But...

552
00:42:31,520 --> 00:42:33,360
she never told me.

553
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:35,080
Why would she?

554
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:40,880
You're just a toy she's having fun with.

555
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:44,400
Lada won't tell you until she graduates.

556
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:48,320
And that's the reality awaiting you.

557
00:42:52,160 --> 00:42:53,640
If you break up with Lada,

558
00:42:55,840 --> 00:42:59,600
I promise to give your mother the best treatment.

559
00:43:00,960 --> 00:43:02,320
You have to choose

560
00:43:03,160 --> 00:43:04,920
between your mother's life

561
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:08,960
and the love that's not real.

562
00:43:55,680 --> 00:43:56,680
Earn!

563
00:43:58,080 --> 00:43:59,840
Why didn't you tell me you were back?

